<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='455171' id='t-455171'>is that this graph here is showing you</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='457196' id='t-457196'>that the biggest correlation with corruption is wealth.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='461161' id='t-461161'>When you're poor, corruption is not your biggest priority.</span>
