<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='467820' id='t-467820'>you'll see the per capita GDP,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='469543' id='t-469543'>basically every country</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='471368' id='t-471368'>with a per capita GDP of, say, less than 5,000 dollars,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='474863' id='t-474863'>has got a corruption score</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='477083' id='t-477083'>of roughly, what's that, about three?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='480118' id='t-480118'>Three out of 10. That's not good.</span>
