<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='495163' id='t-495163'>You see the middle class grow.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='497355' id='t-497355'>And the way to do that is to invest,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='500842' id='t-500842'>not to say I'm not investing in that continent</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='504222' id='t-504222'>because there's too much corruption.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:37
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='506499' id='t-506499'>Now, I don't want to be an apologist for corruption.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='509176' id='t-509176'>I've been arrested because I refused to pay a bribe --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='512115' id='t-512115'>not in Africa, actually.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='514227' id='t-514227'>But what I'm saying here is that</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='515925' id='t-515925'>we can make a difference</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='517715' id='t-517715'>and we can do that by investing.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:51
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='520621' id='t-520621'>Now I'm going to let you in on a little not-so-secret.</span>
