<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='529107' id='t-529107'>And if you go back to the year 2000,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='531631' id='t-531631'>what you'll find is The Economist</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='533394' id='t-533394'>had a very famous cover, &quot;The Hopeless Continent,&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='536562' id='t-536562'>and what they'd done is they'd looked at growth</span>
