<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='562997' id='t-562997'>That new cover shows, well, Africa rising,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='565980' id='t-565980'>because the growth over the last 10 years</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='567707' id='t-567707'>has been about five and a half percent.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:41
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='570327' id='t-570327'>I would like to see if you can all now become economists,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='573853' id='t-573853'>because if growth for the last 10 years</span>
