<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='632891' id='t-632891'>And then something happened in 1980.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='634665' id='t-634665'>Boom! India began to explode.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='636888' id='t-636888'>It wasn't a &quot;Hindu rate of growth,&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='639172' id='t-639172'>&quot;democracies can't grow.&quot; Actually India could.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='642228' id='t-642228'>And if I lay sub-Saharan growth</span>
