<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='668675' id='t-668675'>I can draw out some forecasts</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='670852' id='t-670852'>for the next 30 to 40 years</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='673172' id='t-673172'>which I think are better</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='675242' id='t-675242'>than the ones where you're looking backwards.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='678094' id='t-678094'>And that tells me this:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='680441' id='t-680441'>that Africa is going to go</span>
