<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='715244' id='t-715244'>&quot;Charlie, why are you so pessimistic?&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='720112' id='t-720112'>And you know what?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='721955' id='t-721955'>Actually, I think they've got a point.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='724344' id='t-724344'>Am I really saying that there can be nothing learned,</span>
